snippet.title: Amber Heard ‘Shocked’ She’s Being Called A Liar Amid Johnny Depp Allegations
snippet.description:
I created this video with the YouTube Slideshow Creator (http://www.youtube.cAnd the plot thickens! The Amber Heard and Johnny Depp divorce drama just keeps getting worse. After Amber accused the actor of domestic abuse, people have been wondering if she’s lying, and she’s ‘shocked’ and ‘horrified,’ an insider tells HollywoodLife.com.
After Amber Heard, 30, filed for divorce from Johnny Depp, 52, on May 23, scary details about their relationship have been emerging. The actress obtained a restraining order on May 27, and accused Johnny of abusing her! Johnny is out of the country promoting his new film and can’t defend himself, but that hasn’t stopped fans from stepping in on his behalf and calling Amber a liar! Sadly, she is “shocked” and “horrified” by this.
